Home

Evaluations

   Evaluations are central to the activity of Hcéres. Demanding and
   constructive, they provide a tool at the service of evaluated
   institutions

Indicators & Analyses

   Insightful analyses to contribute to the strategic thinking of
   stakeholders and to the evaluation of public policies

Scientific integrity

   A culture and value to be shared for renewed trust between Science and
   Society

International

   A varied range of services to provide Hcéres expertise in Europe and
   around the word

